maintenance
===========

clean up stale undo files:
    perl -MPath::Tiny -E 'for (path("~/.vim/tmp/undo")->children(qr/^%/)) { $_->remove if ! path($_->basename =~ tr[%][/]r)->exists }'

submodule management
====================

add new plugin:
    cd $REPO
    # example
    git submodule add git://github.com/mileszs/ack.vim.git .vim/bundle/ack
    git submodule init
    git commit -m "..." .gitmodules .vim/bundle/ack

update plugins:
    git submodule -q foreach git pull -q -r -s theirs origin master
    # or add this to crontab:
    @weekly cd $REPO && git submodule -q foreach git pull -q -r -s theirs origin master && git submodule summary && vim -c Helptags -c q >/dev/null 2>&1

remove plugin:
    cd $REPO
    PLUGIN=ack  # example
    git submodule deinit -f .vim/bundle/$PLUGIN
    git rm -f .vim/bundle/$PLUGIN
    rm -rf .git/modules/.vim/bundle/$PLUGIN


